    public class SumPlusOne
extends org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.aggregation.functions.sum.SumVertexProperty
    An aggregate function used for aggregation tests. This function extends the sum aggregate function by a post-processing step incrementing the result by 1L. The expected result of this aggregation is the same as SumVertexProperty (+1). This function can therefore be used to check that the post-processing function is run once and only once.
